    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT PP Presisi Tbk operates as an integrated heavy equipment-based construction company in Indonesia. It engages in civil work projects, including toll road projects, dams, airports, ports, and other projects; civil works comprising earthworks, cut and fill, soil structure improvement, road pavement, concrete, and rigid/flexible pavement; production plant business activities, such as production of ready-mixed concrete and aggregate; mining services; structural work, which consists of construction/foundation buildings such as excavation of soil and hardening the soil structures, and formwork services; and equipment rental, which include tower cranes, passenger hoists, crawler cranes, generator sets and formwork scaffolding, including the operators of heavy equipment. PT PP Presisi Tbk was formerly known as PT PP Peralatan Konstruksi and changed its name to PT PP Presisi Tbk in March 2017. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT PP Presisi Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT PP (Persero) Tbk.",
